'''The Violet Viska''' was a [[Cantina/Legends|cantina]] in the city of [[Ariana]] on [[Garos IV]]. It was so named due to a large sculpture of a [[Viska (species)|Viska]] over the entrance. It had a [[Baragwin/Legends|Baragwin]] bartender and a layer of grease over all of the interior surfaces.

==Appearances==
